{"tid":2190920,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚黃早：Beans䇺子all day breakfast","createTime":"2020-09-06T05:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T15:33:23.000Z","uid":76712,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82175b2d28670df5a4075b8070b89534d60e6256","tid":2190920,"uid":76712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T81DV3h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT81DV3h.png&h=025b6712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑松露炒蛋好香好滑<br />\n三文魚煙肉腸仔樣樣齊，仲要每樣兩舊，份量十足<br />\nSignature pancake最出色<br />\n熱辣辣新鮮整出黎<br />\n配cream cheese一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n杯ice black亦都surprisingly good<br />\n係將軍澳區黎講算好stand out<br />\n（因為本身將軍澳區得垃圾coffee shop）<br />\n整體黎講性價比好高<br />\n咁大份早餐連iced black先$78蚊，好撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難怪周庭BB都要加持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333636b31a47bea499d752feec8ca10f434aa22d","tid":2190920,"uid":322642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514c82cce061d2416343150f0fe4c664b68aa4e5","tid":2190920,"uid":76712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNiyK1m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNiyK1m.png&h=4023f176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n堂食相好似presentable好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm